# Important Concepts

## Flask

A lightweight Python web framework used to build web applications.

---

## Werkzeug

A WSGI library used internally by Flask.

Handles:

- HTTP Requests
- HTTP Responses
- Routing
- Debugging

---

## Virtual Environment

Creates an isolated Python environment for each project.

Advantages

- No package conflicts
- Safe installation
- Industry standard

---

## Debug Mode

```python
app.run(debug=True)
```

Advantages

- Automatically reloads after code changes
- Displays detailed error messages
- Faster development

